column2: Me and Mr. Leo 5x7 inch Picture Frame, Solid Wood High Definition Glass for Table Top Display and Wall Mounting Photo Frame
Create: This simple, classic photo frame creates an entryway that's stylish, a pratical item to display art and photo prints of friends, family, vacations, and more.
Design: This modern minimalist style photo frame for home decor makes you feel at home and can give guests a friendly welcome without so much as a word and sets the tone for your entire home.
Material: The frame is made of solid wood, durable and environmentally friendly. Clear high definition real glass protect your photos from dust, moisture and scratches.
Multifunction: Includes an easel-back for displaying on a shelf or table top as well as hooks for hanging on the wall.
Occasion: Preserving those wonderful memorial, suitable for different occasions like Wedding, Anniversary, Birthday and Various Festivals, perfect gift for family and friends.
Size: Fits 5x7 inch Photos,Actual Frame size (finished size) is 6.5"*4.5"*1.2". With a depth of 1.2", the frame can also be usded as a toy collection display.
Note: Comes with a real glass face, if it is damaged during transportation, please contact us for replacement, we will reply within 24 hours.
